data.description: Let's Get You Home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits quietly on a geese-filled lake along a preserve in this cute little neighborhood tucked away off New Berlin Rd.  With large rooms and a primary suite clear on the other side of the house from the other 3, there is room for privacy and large gatherings!   The newly laid vinyl flooring in the bedrooms and tile throughout the rest of the home, makes it easy to keep the place clean! The back patio overlooks the lake and preserve where you can view some wildlife while enjoying your morning coffee or evening wine! Perfect setting for all preferences! The 2-car garage is large enough for a workspace as well as both vehicles! BRAND NEW ROOF!! Come check out your new home today!
